Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}いつもキミは裏表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.90,ED_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}你总是表里不一
