Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.46,ED_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}独自在意着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}せつないだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.38,ED_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}也只会徒增伤悲
